Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 是这里没错吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这个医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.80,0:03:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}病房之光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又年轻又漂亮的护士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 好像是要被送进地狱的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.50,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着啊 我可不是因为她年轻貌美才不想让她下地狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.80,0:03:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得去阻止被逼得走投无路才寻求地狱少女的人不太好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在说这种话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不认同复仇的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.90,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱木加奈子 二十三岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业于都立上等护士学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.10,0:04:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住址是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有不好的传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.20,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子很孝顺 又认真工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里经济情况不好就放弃读大学读护士学校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱情况呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你眼光不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她说会影响工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找她也都不会同意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.50,0:05:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 那么好的女孩现在很少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母是不可能有什么问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有其父必有其子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有没有招人记恨的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有 不可能有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒唐的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去上班了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我上晚班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来大叔你有按时吃饭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老是担心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操心一下你自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.10,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有什么事就马上来医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:05:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 是好孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论问谁都是一无所获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然问题在医院里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田一先生 今早住院的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么自己觉得不舒服的地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉胃有点不消化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人担心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养病要保持心情舒畅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话非常正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忧心忡忡的 要积极地对待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.80,0:06:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么不明白的话请尽管开口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子妹妹 我肚子也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 一会就给山田先生你打针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.00,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.80,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格也很好 真想一辈子住院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.80,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张床的老爷爷昨天也是这么说着去世的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她那么可爱 会不会被同事嫉妒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.80,0:07:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有就是没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是樱木小姐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫又
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男性患者两个里面就有一个来问樱木小姐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有男朋友吗之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜欢什么样的男生之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是他们的同类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你们看出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.80,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你们同事之间会不太喜欢她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她工作能干人又很热情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热情啊热情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸无城府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.70,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然工作很辛苦 不过托她的福我们轻松很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.50,0:08:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜欢她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是一无所获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁想把她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人真是不可貌相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是她也不知道她暗地里在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的不是那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一看人不准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你女儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不肖女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不要介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱木小姐 不介意的话你也吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.10,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算是替小女向你赔罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 规定上是不允许拿病人东西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.10,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这样子那记者也摸不着头脑了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次他应该没法妨碍我们了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可怜的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因果就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.90,0:10:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在犹豫吗 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 那可不是大人该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.40,0:10:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫负责的出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你们说也没用 叫负责的出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.80,0:10:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}护士中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.10,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是关于这件事我们已经解释过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.70,0:10:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口先生 我们的解释里完全没有谎言或是编造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和您说过很多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.70,0:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您太太是因为回天乏术才去世的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了起诉这家医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和不少律师谈过 可是谁都不好好听我说就拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 是你从中作梗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有这样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的失误 良子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们听到了争吵声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樋口先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.90,0:11:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一口认定他太太的去世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为樱木小姐的失误造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恩将仇报啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论其他人怎么说 我这辈子绝对不会原谅你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会把你送下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.70,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.20,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.30,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是自由记者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于您夫人的死能不能问您些问题呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论问谁都是一无所获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩将仇报啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.40,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.70,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫 小鸫 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.20,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口先生有关良子太太的事我已经尽全力调查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那发现什么决定性证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的主张是没有道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那么你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不中听的话你就充耳不闻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.10,0:14:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我怎么调查 医院和樱木看护师都没有过错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口先生 一切都是你自己想出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 是他们委托你来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个医院好卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给了你多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想来敲诈我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.40,0:15:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口先生 您失去了太太确实很难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太太也死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您丧妻的心情我很理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.10,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是伤害无罪的人来发泄你的痛苦是不对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说错了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有孩子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.60,0:15:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子就是人生的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.40,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没奢望什么只是两个人一起慢慢变老就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.10,0:15:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的感受能向谁说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人 是那个女人不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口先生 是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你登录了地狱通信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托地狱少女对樱木看护师复仇的是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要再装傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.20,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登录 你在说互联网吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧我对那个完全不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.60,0:16:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧好像退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还不舒服的话就让儿科的医生来帮你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.90,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.00,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.90,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那个爷爷冲你发火的时候我看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.20,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叔叔是个寂寞的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.90,0:17:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相伴很久的太太突然不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他受不了那份痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以其实不是个可怕的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情医院里常有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.60,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果冲着我发火樋口先生能心里舒服一点的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那也是我工作的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.90,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你会被送下地狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人被送进地狱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在船上漂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正把你送往地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱 不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么要把我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.40,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 谁做了这事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.10,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.30,0:19:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识 我见都没见过他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.70,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁 为什么要这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.10,0:20:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人难受的工作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.10,0:20:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这几百年里也发生了好几次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨的形式各有不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.90,0:20:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽了职责的小姐真是不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.60,0:20:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我的耳朵能听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.30,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐的内心挣扎的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.10,0:20:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.10,0:21:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.70,0:21:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为这种来历不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.80,0:21:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知所思的人的牺牲品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.70,0:21:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.20,0:21:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还认为复仇是正确的行为吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.20,0:21:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你也还要帮地狱少女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:21:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.00,0:22:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.00,0:22:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.50,0:22:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.20,0:22:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.60,0:22:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.80,0:22:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.70,0:22:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.50,0:22:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.20,0:22:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.70,0:22:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识仙太郎吗
